wikipedia_page.main: Scott Liam Elstone (born 10 June 1990 in Burton-on-Trent, Staffordshire) is an English cricketer. He is a right-handed batsman and bowls right arm off break. He has played for Nottinghamshire, the Unicorns and Derbyshire.
